"recipe.ar_locro.info" = "Locro is Argentina’s iconic patriotic stew, slow-simmered until thick and comforting with hominy, beans, squash, and a mix of meats like beef, pork, and chorizo. Traditionally served steaming hot on national holidays and winter gatherings, it’s finished at the table with a bright, spicy salsa that cuts through the richness and perfumes each bowl.";
