"recipe.ar_parrillada.drink.body" = "Malbec is the quintessential pairing for a parrillada, standing up to char, fat, and sausage spice, while a peppery Bonarda also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lemon or cold yerba mate to refresh between bites.";
