"recipe.ar_provoleta.drink.body" = "A dry Torrontes or crisp Chardonnay pairs well with the salty, smoky cheese and herbs, while a cold lager is also traditional at an asado. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lemon or cold yerba mate.";
