"recipe.at_apfelstrudel.drink.body" = "Pair with an Austrian sweet wine such as Beerenauslese or a late-harvest white that complements apples and cinnamon without overpowering the delicate pastry. A wheat beer can also work for a lighter pairing. For a non-alcoholic option, serve black tea, coffee, or sparkling water.";
