"recipe.at_backhendl.drink.body" = "Pair with a crisp Austrian Grüner Veltliner that stays fresh against fried chicken and vinegar-dressed salad. A pale lager also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lemon or a chilled apple spritz.";
