"recipe.at_salzburger_nockerl.drink.body" = "Pair with an Austrian sweet wine such as Auslese that complements the light sweetness and pairs well with berries. A wheat beer can also work. For a non-alcoholic option, serve coffee, black tea, or sparkling water.";
