"recipe.at_tafelspitz.info" = "Tafelspitz is a classic Austrian dish of beef simmered gently in a clear, aromatic broth until tender, then sliced and served with its broth, roast potatoes, and the traditional accompaniments of apple horseradish and chive sauce. The meat is kept succulent by poaching at a bare simmer, and the sides provide sharp, creamy, and hearty contrasts.";
