"recipe.at_topfenstrudel.info" = "Topfenstrudel is a traditional Austrian strudel filled with a lightly sweetened topfen (quark) mixture, often enriched with egg and scented with lemon, then baked in thin stretched strudel dough until crisp. Served warm and dusted with sugar, it is classically accompanied by vanilla sauce, which complements the tangy, creamy filling.";
