"recipe.au_chicken_parmigiana.info" = "Chicken Parmigiana is a traditional Australian pub main of breaded chicken schnitzel topped with tomato sauce, ham, and melted cheese, then baked and served hot with chips and salad. It is a staple of hotel bistros and casual family dining across Australia.";
