"recipe.au_lamington.info" = "Lamington is a traditional Australian dessert made from squares of sponge cake coated in a thin chocolate icing and rolled in desiccated coconut. It is a classic bakery and fundraiser treat, commonly served at room temperature with tea or coffee.";
