"recipe.au_lamington.step7.body" = "Place the coated lamingtons on a wire rack and leave them until the icing is set.";
"recipe.au_lamington.step7.title" = "Set the coating";
"recipe.au_lamington.step8.body" = "Serve the lamingtons at room temperature.";
