"recipe.au_sticky_date_pudding.info" = "Sticky Date Pudding is a traditional Australian dessert of moist date sponge baked and served warm with a rich butterscotch sauce. It is a classic restaurant and family dessert across Australia, especially in cooler months and at festive gatherings.";
