"recipe.be_tomate_crevettes.info" = "Tomate-crevettes is a classic Belgian brasserie starter: ripe tomatoes hollowed out and filled with North Sea grey shrimp bound in a simple mayonnaise-based salad, traditionally finished with lemon and parsley. It is typically served chilled on a plate with crisp lettuce and a portion of fries and mayonnaise on the side in the brasserie style.";
