"recipe.br_carne_de_sol_com_macaxeira.drink.body" = "A medium-bodied red like Tempranillo pairs well with the salty, buttery beef and the starchy cassava. If you prefer white, a crisp Chardonnay without heavy oak can hold up to the richness. Non-alcoholic pairing: cold cashew juice or sparkling water with lemon.";
