"recipe.br_frango_com_quiabo.drink.body" = "A light red like Pinot Noir pairs nicely with the savory chicken and herbaceous okra without overpowering the dish. If you prefer white, a crisp Sauvignon Blanc complements the tomato-garlic base. Non-alcoholic pairing: chilled sugarcane juice or sparkling water with lime.";
