"recipe.br_pudim_de_leite.drink.body" = "A floral dessert wine such as Muscat complements the caramel and creamy custard without tasting harsh. For a contrasting option, a light tawny-style fortified wine also works well. Non-alcoholic pairing: strong black coffee or cold milk.";
