"recipe.br_quindim.drink.body" = "A rich dessert wine like Sauternes pairs beautifully with the intense egg yolk sweetness and coconut, echoing caramel notes from the baked surface. A lightly chilled fortified wine can also work well. Non-alcoholic pairing: strong black coffee or espresso to balance the sweetness.";
"recipe.br_quindim.drink.summary" = "Dessert wine (Sauternes)";
