"recipe.ca_blueberry_grunt.info" = "Blueberry grunt is a traditional Atlantic Canadian dessert, especially associated with Nova Scotia, made by simmering blueberries on the stovetop and steaming soft biscuit dumplings directly on top. It is a home-style summer dessert usually served warm, often with cold cream.";
