"recipe.ca_butter_tart.info" = "Butter tart is a classic Canadian dessert of flaky pastry filled with a rich mixture of butter, brown sugar, syrup, egg, and dried currants. It is traditionally baked in small tart shells and served at holiday tables, bake sales, and family gatherings across Canada.";
