"recipe.ca_pouding_chomeur.info" = "Pouding Chômeur is a traditional Quebec dessert of simple white cake baked under a hot maple and cream sauce that settles into a rich syrupy layer. It is closely associated with sugar shack season and home-style family meals, and it is traditionally served warm.";
