"recipe.cl_pastel_de_choclo.drink.body" = "Pair with a medium-bodied Chilean Carménère or Merlot to match the beef and sweet-savory contrast. A dry rosé is also a good fit. Non-alcoholic option: sparkling water with lemon or a chilled iced tea with citrus.";
