"recipe.cl_porotos_granados.drink.body" = "Pair with a crisp Chilean Sauvignon Blanc or a dry rosé that complements sweet corn and basil while keeping the dish feeling fresh. A light lager also works well. Non-alcoholic option: sparkling water with lime or a chilled herbal tea such as mint or lemon verbena.";
