"recipe.cn_ba_bao_fan.info" = "Ba bao fan is a traditional Chinese festive dessert of steamed glutinous rice enriched with lard and sugar, layered with sweet red bean paste, and decorated with dried fruits, nuts, and seeds in a patterned bowl. It is commonly served warm at Lunar New Year banquets and family celebrations for luck and abundance.";
