"recipe.cu_ropa_vieja.info" = "Cuban ropa vieja is a traditional shredded beef dish where braised beef is pulled into strands and simmered in a rich sofrito of onion, bell pepper, garlic, tomato, and spices. It is served hot as a staple home-style main, traditionally accompanied by white rice and frijoles negros to soak up the savory sauce.";
