"recipe.cu_vaca_frita.info" = "Cuban vaca frita is a classic dish of beef simmered until tender, shredded, then pan-fried until crisp with onions, garlic, and plenty of lime. It is served hot as a staple Cuban home-style main, traditionally alongside white rice and frijoles negros to balance the bright citrus and savory, crispy beef.";
