"recipe.de_schwarzwalder_kirschtorte.info" = "Schwarzwälder Kirschtorte is the classic German Black Forest cake: layers of cocoa sponge soaked with Kirschwasser, filled with sour cherries and clouds of whipped cream, then finished with more cream, chocolate shavings, and cherries on top. It is served well chilled so the layers hold cleanly, with the unmistakable pairing of chocolate, cherry, and kirsch.";
