"recipe.dz_chakhchoukha.step8.body" = "Tear the cooked sheets into pieces, place in a steamer, and steam until tender and pliable, fluffing once or twice so it steams evenly.";
"recipe.dz_chakhchoukha.step8.title" = "Steam the bread to soften";
