"recipe.dz_chorba_frik.info" = "Chorba Frik is a traditional Algerian soup made with lamb simmered in a tomato-rich broth with chickpeas, celery, and warm spices, thickened with frik (cracked green wheat) that cooks into a hearty, comforting texture. It is a classic starter, especially during Ramadan, served steaming hot with homemade Algerian bread for dipping and soaking up the fragrant broth.";
"recipe.dz_chorba_frik.info.summary" = "Freekeh lamb soup";
