"recipe.eg_ful_medames.drink.body" = "Pair with a crisp, dry white wine such as Sauvignon Blanc to lift the lemon and garlic and cut through the olive oil. A light lager also works well with the savory beans. Non-alcoholic option: mint tea or sparkling water with lemon.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.drink.summary" = "White wine (Sauvignon)";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.info" = "Ful medames is Egypt’s classic slow-cooked fava bean dish, traditionally made by soaking and simmering dried fava beans until creamy, then roughly mashing and seasoning with garlic, cumin, lemon, salt, and olive oil. It is served warm with chopped onion, tomato, and parsley, alongside hard-boiled eggs and baladi-style bread for scooping, making a hearty everyday meal from breakfast through supper.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.info.summary" = "Egyptian fava staple";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.name" = "Ful medames";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step1.body" = "Rinse %i1 and cover with plenty of %i2 in a bowl. Soak until fully hydrated.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step1.title" = "Soak the fava beans";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step2.body" = "Drain the beans, place them in a pot, and cover with fresh water. Bring up slowly to a gentle simmer.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step2.title" = "Start simmering the beans";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step3.body" = "Simmer gently until the beans are very tender and creamy, topping up with water as needed to keep them covered and stirring occasionally so they do not catch.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step3.title" = "Cook until creamy";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step4.body" = "Boil %i12 until hard, cool them, peel, and set aside for serving.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step4.title" = "Boil the eggs";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step5.body" = "Finely chop %i9, dice %i10, and chop %i11. Crush %i4.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step5.title" = "Prepare the garnishes";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step6.body" = "Drain the beans, reserving some cooking liquid. Mash the beans to a coarse cream, loosening with a little cooking liquid. Mix in garlic, %i5, %i8, %i7, and %i6 until glossy and well balanced.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step6.title" = "Mash and season the ful";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step7.body" = "Spoon the ful into bowls and top with onion, tomatoes, and parsley. Serve with hard-boiled eggs and %i13 alongside.";
"recipe.eg_ful_medames.step7.title" = "Serve";
