"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.drink.body" = "Pair with a crisp, mineral dry white such as Albariño or Txakoli to cut through the rich olive-oil emulsion and complement the cod. A clean, lightly bitter lager also works well. Non-alcoholic option: sparkling water with lemon.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.drink.summary" = "White wine (Albariño)";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.info" = "Bacalao al pil-pil is a traditional Basque dish of desalted cod gently confited in garlic- and guindilla-infused olive oil, then emulsified into a glossy sauce using the cod’s natural gelatin. Served hot with the silky pil-pil spooned over the fish, it’s a celebrated northern Spanish classic typically eaten with crusty bread to mop up the sauce.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.info.summary" = "Basque cod in pil-pil";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.name" = "Cod pil-pil";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step1.body" = "Rinse %i1 and place it in a container. Cover completely with cold %i2 and refrigerate.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step1.title" = "Start desalting the cod";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step2.body" = "Keep the cod refrigerated, changing the water several times so the fish becomes pleasantly seasoned rather than salty. Drain well when ready.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step2.title" = "Desalt until balanced";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step3.body" = "Pat the cod very dry and cut into even pieces if needed, keeping the skin on.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step3.title" = "Dry and portion";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step4.body" = "Pour %i3 into a wide shallow pan over low heat. Add thinly sliced %i4 and %i5 and gently warm until the garlic turns pale golden, then lift out garlic and chile with a slotted spoon and reserve.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step4.title" = "Infuse the olive oil";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step5.body" = "Lower the heat so the oil barely trembles. Add the cod pieces and cook gently, turning carefully so they cook through without frying and begin releasing their juices.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step5.title" = "Gently cook the cod";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step6.body" = "Remove the pan from direct heat to keep the oil gentle. Move the pan in steady circular motions so the cod juices emulsify with the oil into a thick, glossy pil-pil sauce.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step6.title" = "Emulsify the pil-pil";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step7.body" = "Return the reserved garlic and guindilla to the pan. Spoon the pil-pil over the cod and serve immediately with %i6.";
"recipe.es_bacalao_al_pil_pil.step7.title" = "Finish and serve";
