"recipe.et_beyaynetu.info" = "Beyaynetu is the traditional Ethiopian vegetarian platter served on injera, featuring a variety of richly seasoned stews and vegetables arranged together for sharing. It is commonly enjoyed during fasting periods and in everyday meals, with each component eaten by tearing pieces of injera to scoop up the different wats and greens in one bite.";
