"recipe.et_kitfo.step4.title" = "Rest the batter";
"recipe.et_kitfo.step5.body" = "Heat a nonstick skillet over medium heat. Ladle in batter and swirl to coat. Cover to steam until the top sets and the edges lift, then remove to cool. Repeat to use up the batter.";
