"recipe.ge_gebzhalia.info" = "Gebzhalia is a traditional Megrelian Georgian starter made from softened sulguni cheese rolled around a fresh cheese and mint filling, then served sliced in a cool matsoni-based sauce. It is commonly presented as part of a supra table with other cold appetizers, especially in western Georgia.";
