"recipe.ge_khinkali.info" = "Khinkali are traditional Georgian pleated dumplings filled with seasoned meat, onion, herbs, and broth-forming liquid, then boiled and served hot. They are a classic main dish, especially in mountain-style taverns and family gatherings, eaten by hand and finished with black pepper.";
