"recipe.ge_mtsvadi.info" = "Mtsvadi is a traditional Georgian dish of large cubes of pork skewered and grilled over hot coals until smoky, juicy, and lightly charred. It is served hot as a main dish at family gatherings and outdoor feasts, traditionally with sliced onions and tkemali sauce.";
