"recipe.gr_pastitsio.drink.body" = "Pair with a medium-bodied Greek red such as Agiorgitiko that suits tomato, cinnamon, and minced meat. A dry rosé also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lemon or a chilled herbal iced tea.";
"recipe.gr_pastitsio.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Agiorgitiko)";
"recipe.gr_pastitsio.info" = "Pastitsio is a classic Greek baked pasta casserole built in layers: tubular pasta bound with egg and cheese, a rich cinnamon-scented minced meat and tomato sauce, and a thick béchamel topping baked until golden. It is served hot in squares after resting so the layers set, making it a staple home and taverna main.";
