"recipe.gr_stifado.drink.body" = "Pair with a medium-bodied Greek red such as Agiorgitiko that complements warm spices and braised beef. A dry rosé also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water or a tart pomegranate spritz.";
"recipe.gr_stifado.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Agiorgitiko)";
