"recipe.gr_tzatziki.drink.body" = "Pair with a crisp Greek white such as Assyrtiko or a dry rosé that stays fresh with garlic, cucumber, and yogurt. A light lager also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lemon or a chilled lemon soda.";
