"recipe.gr_tzatziki.info" = "Tzatziki is a classic Greek meze of thick strained yogurt mixed with grated cucumber that has been well-drained, garlic, olive oil, and a touch of vinegar, finished with dill. It is served chilled as a dip with bread and also as a staple accompaniment to grilled meats, where its cool tang balances rich, smoky flavors.";
