"recipe.hk_bo_zai_fan.info" = "A traditional Cantonese claypot rice dish from Hong Kong, cooked in a clay pot to create fragrant rice and a prized crispy crust at the bottom. It is typically served hot with preserved meats and a seasoned soy sauce poured over just before eating.";
