"recipe.hu_palacsinta_gundel.drink.body" = "Pair with a sweet Tokaji that complements walnuts, cocoa, and rum notes without feeling heavy. A strong coffee can also work alongside. For a non-alcoholic option, serve espresso, black tea, or sparkling water.";
