"recipe.hu_paprikas_csirke.info" = "Csirkepaprikás is a classic Hungarian paprika chicken stew: chicken pieces are braised with lots of onions in a sweet-paprika base, then finished with sour cream for a silky, orange-red sauce. It is traditionally served with nokedli, small dumplings that catch the rich sauce, making it a staple home-cooked main.";
