"recipe.hu_rakott_krumpli.info" = "Rakott krumpli is a traditional Hungarian layered potato casserole of sliced potatoes, hard-boiled eggs, and kolbász sausage, bound with sour cream and baked until bubbling and golden. It is served hot after a short rest so the layers hold together, making a classic family-style main.";
