"recipe.hu_turos_csusza.info" = "Túrós csusza is a classic Hungarian comfort dish of broad egg noodles tossed with túró (Hungarian curd cheese), sour cream, and crispy fried bacon, with some bacon fat used to enrich the pasta. It is served hot so the cheese softens and coats the noodles, balancing tangy dairy with smoky, crunchy bacon.";
