"recipe.id_ayam_betutu.info" = "Ayam betutu is a traditional Balinese whole chicken dish rubbed and stuffed with a rich bumbu betutu spice paste, then slowly cooked until fragrant and tender before finishing over dry heat. It is commonly served for family meals and festive gatherings, with hot rice and a fresh chili-shallot sambal on the side.";
