"recipe.id_bubur_sumsum.info" = "Bubur sumsum is a traditional Indonesian dessert of silky rice flour porridge cooked with coconut milk and pandan, served warm or at room temperature with a fragrant palm sugar syrup. It is commonly enjoyed as a snack or sweet breakfast and is especially popular at markets and family gatherings.";
