"recipe.id_lapis_legit.info" = "Lapis legit is a traditional Indonesian layered butter cake influenced by Dutch colonial baking, built from many thin baked layers enriched with egg yolks, butter, and warm spices. It is commonly served in small slices for celebrations, holidays, and formal visits, often alongside tea or coffee.";
