"recipe.in_kheer.info" = "Rice kheer is a classic Indian milk pudding made by slowly simmering rice in milk with sugar until thick and creamy, then perfumed with cardamom and finished with nuts and raisins. It is traditionally served warm or chilled at family meals, festivals, and religious celebrations.";
