"recipe.ir_kabab_barg.info" = "Kabab Barg is a refined Iranian kebab of very thinly sliced, tender beef or lamb, marinated with onion and saffron, then grilled quickly over hot coals. It is traditionally served with chelo rice, butter, grilled tomatoes, and sumac, often alongside fresh herbs and flatbread.";
