"recipe.ir_kashk_e_bademjan.info" = "Kashk-e Bademjan is a classic Iranian appetizer of roasted or fried eggplant mashed with sautéed onions and garlic, finished with tangy kashk and topped with mint-garlic oil and crisp fried onions. It is traditionally served warm or at room temperature with Persian flatbread, often as part of a mezze-style spread.";
