"recipe.ir_khoresh_fesenjan.drink.body" = "A light to medium-bodied red such as Pinot Noir complements the sweet-tart pomegranate and nutty depth without overwhelming it. If you prefer white, choose an aromatic off-dry Riesling to match the gentle sweetness. Non-alcoholic: doogh (yogurt-mint drink) or sparkling water with lime.";
