"recipe.ir_khoresh_fesenjan.info" = "Khoresht-e Fesenjan is a classic Iranian stew made by slowly cooking ground walnuts until their oils enrich the sauce, then simmering poultry in a deep, glossy pomegranate base that turns sweet-tart and dark. It is traditionally served as a khoresh alongside fluffy Persian steamed rice, making it a special-occasion dish known for its distinctive color and rich, velvety texture.";
