"recipe.ir_mast_o_khiar.info" = "Mast-o Khiar is a classic Iranian yogurt and cucumber dish mixed with fragrant herbs and a gentle seasoning, often finished with walnuts and raisins for texture and sweetness. It is served chilled as a refreshing starter or side, commonly set on the table alongside grilled dishes and rice, and eaten with Persian flatbread.";
