"recipe.ir_mirza_ghasemi.drink.body" = "Aromatic whites such as Viognier or dry Riesling complement smoky eggplant, garlic, and tomato. If you prefer red, choose a light Pinot Noir served slightly cool. Non-alcoholic: doogh (yogurt-mint drink) or sparkling water with lemon.";
