"recipe.ir_mirza_ghasemi.info" = "Mirza Ghasemi is a classic Northern Iranian dish from Gilan made with fire-roasted eggplant mashed into a garlicky tomato base and finished by gently cooking eggs into the mixture. It is traditionally served warm with Persian flatbread, often as a starter or light meal, prized for its smoky aroma and rich texture.";
