"recipe.ir_zereshk_polo_ba_morgh.drink.body" = "Aromatic whites like dry to off-dry Riesling or Viognier pair well with saffron, tomato sauce, and the barberries’ tartness. If you prefer red, choose a light Pinot Noir served slightly cool. Non-alcoholic: doogh (yogurt-mint drink) or sparkling water with lime.";
