"recipe.it_panettone.drink.summary" = "Moscato d'Asti";
"recipe.it_panettone.info" = "A traditional Italian holiday bread from Milan, enriched with butter, eggs, and sugar, and studded with raisins and candied citrus. Slow rises create a light, shreddable crumb and a tall, domed loaf, typically served in slices at room temperature for Christmas and New Year gatherings.";
