"recipe.it_pasta_all_amatriciana.drink.body" = "Pair with a medium-bodied central Italian red such as Montepulciano d’Abruzzo or a young Cesanese to stand up to guanciale and pecorino. A dry Italian amber beer also works. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water or a bitter orange soda.";
"recipe.it_pasta_all_amatriciana.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Montepulciano)";
