"recipe.it_pasta_all_amatriciana.step7.body" = "Transfer the pasta to the skillet and toss vigorously with the sauce, loosening with a little pasta cooking water if needed.";
"recipe.it_pasta_all_amatriciana.step7.title" = "Finish in the sauce";
