"recipe.jp_okonomiyaki.step7.body" = "Flip once more briefly if needed to crisp the surface and render the pork fully, pressing lightly only to keep the shape even.";
"recipe.jp_okonomiyaki.step7.title" = "Finish on the griddle";
"recipe.jp_okonomiyaki.step8.body" = "Transfer to plates and brush with %i11, drizzle %i12, then sprinkle with %i13 and %i14.";
