"recipe.jp_ramen.info" = "Shoyu ramen is a traditional Japanese noodle soup with springy wheat noodles served in a clear soy-seasoned chicken and pork broth, topped with chashu, menma, nori, scallions, and soft eggs. It is commonly eaten as a hearty everyday meal in ramen shops and at home, served piping hot and assembled just before eating.";
