"recipe.jp_sukiyaki.info" = "Sukiyaki is a traditional Japanese nabemono hot pot of thinly sliced beef, tofu, vegetables, and noodles simmered in a sweet-savory soy warishita broth. It is commonly served as a shared table meal for family gatherings and special occasions, with ingredients cooked at the table and dipped in beaten raw egg before eating.";
