"recipe.jp_sukiyaki.step3.title" = "Prepare the egg dipping bowls";
"recipe.jp_sukiyaki.step4.body" = "Place the sukiyaki pan on the burner and arrange the beef, vegetables, tofu, shirataki, warishita, eggs, and %i17 for shared cooking.";
