"recipe.kh_bor_bor_thnaut.drink.body" = "A lightly sweet white wine such as Moscato pairs well with the creamy coconut and palm sweetness. A mild jasmine tea also works beautifully. For a non-alcoholic option, serve hot pandan tea or unsweetened green tea.";
"recipe.kh_bor_bor_thnaut.drink.summary" = "Sweet wine (Moscato)";
"recipe.kh_bor_bor_thnaut.info" = "Bor bor thnaut is a traditional Cambodian dessert made from glutinous rice cooked into a sweet pudding with toddy palm seeds and coconut, then finished with a rich coconut cream topping. It is commonly served warm as a comforting sweet dish and is especially associated with palm-growing regions.";
