"recipe.kh_samlor_kari.drink.body" = "An aromatic white wine such as Riesling or Gewurztraminer pairs well with the mild curry spices and coconut richness. A pale lager also works very well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve iced jasmine tea or chilled lime water.";
"recipe.kh_samlor_kari.drink.summary" = "White wine (Riesling)";
"recipe.kh_samlor_kari.info" = "Samlor kari is a traditional Cambodian coconut curry, typically made with chicken, red kroeung, and vegetables such as sweet potato, long beans, and eggplant. It is mildly spiced, fragrant, and commonly served for family meals, celebrations, and gatherings, often with bread for dipping and rice on the side.";
