"recipe.lb_hummus.info" = "Lebanese hummus bi tahini is a smooth chickpea and tahini mezze, brightened with lemon and garlic and finished with a generous drizzle of olive oil. It is served at room temperature as part of a shared table, traditionally scooped with warm pita bread alongside other Lebanese dishes.";
"recipe.lb_hummus.info.summary" = "Smooth tahini hummus";
