"recipe.lb_hummus.step1.title" = "Soak the chickpeas";
"recipe.lb_hummus.step2.body" = "Put the soaked chickpeas in a pot, cover with water, and bring to a boil. Skim off any foam, stir in %i3, then simmer until the chickpeas are very soft and easily crushed. Reserve some hot cooking liquid, then drain.";
"recipe.lb_hummus.step2.title" = "Cook until very tender";
