"recipe.lb_mujaddara.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Cinsault)";
"recipe.lb_mujaddara.info" = "Lebanese mujaddara is a comforting dish of lentils and rice cooked together with cumin and finished with a generous topping of deeply caramelized onions. It is served warm or at room temperature, traditionally alongside a simple tomato-cucumber salad, tangy pickles, and plain yogurt.";
