"recipe.lk_kukul_mas_curry.info" = "Kukul mas curry is a traditional Sri Lankan chicken curry made with bone-in chicken simmered with onion, ginger, garlic, curry leaves, roasted curry powder, and coconut milk into a rich aromatic gravy. It is a staple home-style main dish, commonly served hot with rice and other accompaniments.";
