"recipe.mm_shan_khauk_swe.info" = "Shan khauk swe is a traditional Myanmar Shan noodle dish of rice noodles topped with a savory chicken and tomato sauce, garlic oil, and fresh herbs, usually served as a dry mixed noodle bowl with a light broth on the side. It is a popular everyday meal in Shan-style eateries and homes, known for its balanced savory, tangy, and aromatic flavor.";
