"recipe.mm_thoke_son.info" = "Let Thoke Sone is a traditional Myanmar hand-tossed mixed salad built from rice, noodles, potato, crunchy vegetables, and savory toppings, then dressed with fish sauce, tamarind, lime, and aromatic oils. It is commonly served as a street food or casual shared meal, with diners mixing everything by hand just before eating.";
