"recipe.mu_cari_poisson.info" = "Mauritian cari poisson is a homestyle fish curry built on a base of onion, garlic, ginger, tomatoes, curry powder, turmeric, and fresh herbs, simmered just long enough to keep the fish tender. It is traditionally eaten as part of a full plate with steamed rice, a simple lentil dal, and a bright tomato rougaille to balance the curry’s warmth.";
