"recipe.mu_cari_poulet.drink.body" = "A crisp, aromatic white such as Sauvignon Blanc or Chenin Blanc pairs well with the curry spices and tomato base, keeping the meal lively. If you prefer red, choose a light-bodied, low-tannin red served slightly chilled, such as Grenache. Non-alcoholic pairing: chilled sparkling water with lime or ginger-lemon tea.";
