"recipe.mu_cari_poulet.info" = "Mauritian cari poulet is a classic island curry of chicken simmered in a fragrant base of onion, garlic, ginger, tomatoes, curry powder, turmeric, and herbs like thyme and curry leaves, often finished with tender potatoes in the sauce. It is traditionally served as a complete plate with steamed rice, a simple lentil dal (grains), and a fresh tomato rougaille to bring brightness and heat alongside the warm curry.";
