"recipe.mu_vindaye_poulpe.drink.body" = "Choose a zesty white like dry Riesling or Sauvignon Blanc to match the vinegar tang and mustard heat. If you prefer red, opt for a very light, low-tannin red served slightly chilled. Non-alcoholic pairing: sparkling water with lime or chilled ginger tea.";
