"recipe.mx_chiles_en_nogada.drink.body" = "A floral, medium-bodied white such as Viognier or an off-dry Riesling complements the sweet-savory filling and rich walnut sauce. A light, crisp lager also works well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve sparkling water with lime or agua fresca.";
