"recipe.mx_sopa_de_tortilla.drink.body" = "A crisp Sauvignon Blanc or a light, dry rosé pairs well with the tomato-chile broth and fresh garnishes, and a Mexican lager is also a great match. For a non-alcoholic option, serve agua fresca or sparkling water with lime.";
