"recipe.my_asam_pedas_ikan.info" = "Asam pedas ikan is a traditional Malaysian fish stew with a hot and tangy gravy made from chilies, tamarind, and aromatics. It is commonly served as a home-style main dish with steamed rice, especially for lunch or dinner.";
