"recipe.my_ayam_percik.info" = "Ayam percik is a traditional Malaysian grilled chicken dish, especially associated with the east coast, coated and basted with a rich coconut-spice sauce. It is served hot as a main dish, commonly with rice, with extra percik sauce spooned over the chicken.";
"recipe.my_ayam_percik.info.summary" = "Grilled spiced chicken";
