"recipe.my_satay.info" = "Satay is a traditional Malaysian grilled skewered meat dish, commonly made with turmeric-spiced chicken and served with peanut sauce, cucumber, onion, and ketupat rice cakes. It is typically served hot as a main dish or shared platter, especially at gatherings and evening meals.";
