"recipe.ng_banga_soup.drink.body" = "A dry Riesling or crisp Sauvignon Blanc pairs well with the palm-nut richness, smoked fish, and peppery spice without tasting heavy. If you prefer red, choose a light, low-tannin red served slightly chilled. Non-alcoholic pairing: chilled zobo (hibiscus) or sparkling water with lime.";
