"recipe.ng_yam_porridge.drink.body" = "A dry Riesling or crisp Chenin Blanc balances the pepper heat and palm oil richness while staying refreshing. If you prefer red, choose a light, low-tannin red served slightly chilled. Non-alcoholic pairing: chilled zobo (hibiscus) or sparkling water with lime.";
