"recipe.nl_hachee.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Merlot)";
"recipe.nl_hachee.info" = "Hachee is a traditional Dutch beef and onion stew slowly braised until the meat is tender and the onions melt into a thick, sweet-sour gravy. It is characteristically seasoned with cloves, bay, and black pepper and thickened naturally with the long-cooked onions and crumbled ontbijtkoek. It is traditionally served with red cabbage and boiled potatoes.";
