"recipe.nl_hutspot.info" = "Hutspot is a traditional Dutch mash of potatoes, carrots, and onions cooked together and mashed into a rustic stamppot, typically served with braised beef (klapstuk) and melted butter. It is classic winter comfort food, served hot so the mash stays creamy and the meat is tender and warming.";
