"recipe.nl_stamppot_andijvie.info" = "Stamppot andijvie is a traditional Dutch potato mash mixed with raw curly endive so it lightly wilts from the heat, then served with smoked sausage and gravy. The contrast of creamy potatoes and slightly bitter endive is central, and it is classic winter comfort food served steaming hot.";
