"recipe.pe_suspiro_a_la_limena.drink.body" = "Pair with a small glass of tawny Port to echo the port-scented meringue and caramel notes. A sweet Moscatel also pairs well. For a non-alcoholic option, serve strong coffee or black tea to cut the sweetness.";
"recipe.pe_suspiro_a_la_limena.drink.summary" = "Dessert wine (Port)";
"recipe.pe_suspiro_a_la_limena.info" = "Suspiro a la Limeña is a classic Limeño dessert of silky manjar blanco made from sweetened condensed milk and evaporated milk, enriched with egg yolks and vanilla, then topped with a glossy port-scented meringue and a dusting of cinnamon. It is served in individual cups, chilled and rich, with the airy topping balancing the deep caramel sweetness.";
