"recipe.ph_pinakbet.info" = "Pinakbet is a traditional Filipino vegetable stew from the Ilocos region made with mixed vegetables simmered with pork, tomatoes, and fermented shrimp paste until deeply savory and lightly saucy. It is commonly served hot as a main family dish with steamed rice and highlights bitter, sweet, and umami flavors.";
