"recipe.ru_befstroganov.drink.body" = "A light to medium-bodied red such as Pinot Noir or a мягкий Russian-style red pairs well with the creamy sour-cream sauce and sautéed beef. A crisp dry white can also work if you prefer. Non-alcoholic pairing: sparkling water or black tea with lemon.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Pinot Noir)";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.info" = "Beef Stroganoff is a classic Russian dish of quickly sautéed strips of tender beef combined with onions and mushrooms in a tangy sour-cream and mustard sauce. It is served hot, traditionally alongside mashed potatoes, so the creamy sauce can be spooned over both the beef and the potatoes.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.info.summary" = "Russian cream beef";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.name" = "Beef Stroganoff";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step1.body" = "Peel and cut the %i12 into even chunks. Slice %i3 thinly, slice %i2, and cut %i1 into thin strips. Season the beef with %i10 and %i11 and lightly coat it with %i6.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step1.title" = "Prep ingredients";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step2.body" = "Cook the potatoes in salted %i16 until very tender, then drain well and let them steam dry briefly.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step2.title" = "Boil potatoes";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step3.body" = "Warm %i13. Mash the potatoes with %i14 and warm milk until smooth, season with %i15, and keep warm.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step3.title" = "Mash the potatoes";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step4.body" = "Heat a skillet until hot, add %i5, and quickly sear the beef in batches so it browns without steaming. Transfer the beef to a plate.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step4.title" = "Sear the beef";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step5.body" = "In the same skillet, melt %i4 and cook the onion until softened, then add mushrooms and cook until their moisture evaporates and they begin to brown.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step5.title" = "Cook onions and mushrooms";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step6.body" = "Stir in %i9, then add %i7 and bring to a gentle simmer, scraping up any browned bits. Let it thicken into a glossy sauce.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step6.title" = "Build the sauce";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step7.body" = "Lower the heat and stir in %i8 until smooth, keeping it hot but not boiling. Taste and adjust seasoning.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step7.title" = "Finish with sour cream";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step8.body" = "Return the beef and any juices to the sauce and warm through briefly so the beef stays tender. Serve immediately over mashed potatoes.";
"recipe.ru_befstroganov.step8.title" = "Combine and serve";
