"recipe.sa_qursan.info" = "Qursan is a traditional Saudi main dish from Najd made with very thin whole wheat flatbread layered with a rich lamb and vegetable stew. It is a hearty communal meal served hot, with the bread absorbing the savory broth and softening beneath the meat and vegetables on a large serving platter.";
"recipe.sa_qursan.info.summary" = "Bread-soaked stew platter";
