"recipe.sk_bryndzove_halusky.drink.body" = "A fresh white wine such as Riesling pairs well with the salty bryndza and rich bacon without making the dish feel heavy. A pale lager is also a classic match. For a non-alcoholic option, serve kefir or sparkling water.";
