"recipe.sn_mafe.step8.title" = "Cook the vegetables";
"recipe.sn_mafe.step9.body" = "Taste and adjust seasoning, then spoon rice onto plates and ladle the mafé over the top, making sure each serving gets meat, vegetables, and plenty of sauce.";
