"recipe.sy_fatteh.drink.summary" = "White wine (Viognier)";
"recipe.sy_fatteh.info" = "Syrian chickpea fatteh is a traditional layered dish built from crisp bread, hot chickpeas, and a tangy garlic yogurt-tahini sauce, finished with sizzling ghee and toasted nuts. It is commonly served warm for breakfast or as a hearty shared meal, assembled at the last moment so the bread stays crunchy under the creamy topping.";
