"recipe.sy_halawet_el_jibn.drink.body" = "A lightly sweet, aromatic Muscat complements the orange blossom and rose notes, while a late-harvest Riesling also pairs well with the creamy filling. For a non-alcoholic option, serve hot black tea with mint or a cold rosewater lemonade.";
