"recipe.sy_kebab_halabi.step8.body" = "Warm %i9 in a saucepan, add the %i10 and cook gently until fragrant. Stir in the %i12 and cook until it loosens and darkens slightly.";
"recipe.sy_kebab_halabi.step8.title" = "Build the sauce base";
