"recipe.sy_shakriyeh.info" = "Shakriyeh is a traditional Syrian stew of tender lamb simmered in a gently tangy cooked yogurt sauce, typically finished with toasted pine nuts and served over plain rice. It is a classic home and banquet dish, prized for its creamy, balanced tartness and delicate spice.";
"recipe.sy_shakriyeh.info.summary" = "Yogurt lamb stew";
