"recipe.sy_shish_barak.drink.summary" = "White wine (Viognier)";
"recipe.sy_shish_barak.info" = "Shish Barak is a traditional Syrian dish of small meat-filled dumplings, lightly baked then simmered in a tangy cooked yogurt sauce and finished with a garlic-mint ghee topping. It is commonly served as a hearty family meal, often alongside plain rice to balance the creamy, tart broth.";
