"recipe.sy_shish_barak.step5.body" = "Place a small amount of filling in each round, fold to seal, then pinch the ends together to form a small tortellini-like dumpling. Arrange on a tray.";
"recipe.sy_shish_barak.step5.title" = "Fill and shape dumplings";
"recipe.sy_shish_barak.step6.body" = "Bake the dumplings until dry and lightly golden, so they hold their shape in the yogurt sauce.";
"recipe.sy_shish_barak.step6.title" = "Bake the dumplings";
