"recipe.th_khao_soi.info" = "Khao Soi Gai is a traditional Northern Thai coconut curry noodle soup with braised chicken, boiled egg noodles, and a topping of crispy fried noodles. It is served with pickled mustard greens, shallots, lime, and chili oil for balance and is commonly eaten as a complete one-bowl meal.";
