"recipe.tr_ali_nazik_kebabi.drink.body" = "A medium-bodied Syrah or a plush Grenache pairs with the buttery lamb and smoky eggplant, while a soft Merlot can also work. For a non-alcoholic option, serve chilled ayran or sparkling water with lemon.";
"recipe.tr_ali_nazik_kebabi.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Syrah)";
"recipe.tr_ali_nazik_kebabi.info" = "Ali Nazik Kebabı is a traditional dish from Gaziantep featuring smoky roasted eggplant mashed with garlic yogurt, topped with sizzling spiced minced lamb cooked in butter and pepper paste. It is served hot with lavash to scoop up the rich meat and creamy, smoky eggplant base.";
