"recipe.tr_icli_kofte.step4.title" = "Knead the shell dough";
"recipe.tr_icli_kofte.step5.body" = "Pinch off portions of the shell dough, hollow each one into a thin cup, fill with the cooled meat mixture, and seal to form torpedo shapes with pointed ends.";
"recipe.tr_icli_kofte.step5.title" = "Shape and fill";
