"recipe.tr_iskender_kebab.drink.body" = "A medium-bodied Syrah or Grenache pairs well with the tomato-butter sauce and savory meat, while a smooth Merlot also fits. For a non-alcoholic option, serve ayran or sparkling water with lemon.";
"recipe.tr_iskender_kebab.drink.summary" = "Red wine (Syrah)";
"recipe.tr_iskender_kebab.info" = "İskender Kebab is a classic dish from Bursa featuring thinly sliced döner-style meat served over pieces of pide bread, bathed in hot tomato-butter sauce, and finished with strained yogurt on the side. Traditionally the meat is cooked on a vertical spit, then assembled to order so the bread absorbs the sauce while staying tender and rich.";
"recipe.tr_iskender_kebab.info.summary" = "Döner on bread";
