"recipe.tr_karniyarik.info" = "Karnıyarık is a classic Turkish home dish of fried eggplants split open and filled with a savory minced-meat and onion mixture, then baked in a light tomato sauce until the eggplants turn meltingly tender. It is traditionally served hot with pilav and a spoon of plain yogurt on the side.";
