"recipe.tw_lu_rou_fan.step10.body" = "Divide rice into bowls, spoon the braised pork and sauce over the top, add a braised egg and bok choy, and serve hot.";
"recipe.tw_lu_rou_fan.step10.title" = "Assemble bowls";
"recipe.tw_lu_rou_fan.step2.body" = "Rinse the %i12 until the water runs mostly clear, combine with %i13 in a pot, and start cooking covered.";
"recipe.tw_lu_rou_fan.step2.title" = "Start cooking rice";
