"recipe.ua_borshch.step7.title" = "Return the meat and strain the broth";
"recipe.ua_borshch.step8.body" = "Add the potatoes and cabbage to the broth, then after they begin to soften add the cooked beet mixture and the remaining soup salt.";
"recipe.ua_borshch.step8.title" = "Build the borshch";
"recipe.ua_borshch.step9.body" = "Cook the soup gently until the vegetables are tender and the broth becomes sweet, earthy, and deep red.";
