"recipe.ua_deruny.info" = "Ukrainian deruny are traditional potato pancakes made from finely grated potatoes mixed with onion, egg, and flour, then fried until crisp and golden. They are a staple of Ukrainian home cooking, often served for breakfast or supper, and are traditionally eaten hot with sour cream.";
