"recipe.ua_varenyky.info" = "Ukrainian varenyky are traditional boiled dumplings made with a soft unleavened dough and a simple potato and onion filling. They are a staple of Ukrainian home cooking and festive tables, and are traditionally served hot with fried onions and sour cream.";
