"recipe.ve_torta_negra.drink.body" = "Serve with a light sweet dessert wine or a small glass of dark rum that complements the spiced fruit cake. For a non-alcoholic option, serve black coffee or hot black tea.";
"recipe.ve_torta_negra.drink.summary" = "Sweet dessert wine";
"recipe.ve_torta_negra.info" = "Torta negra is the traditional Venezuelan Christmas cake, made from a dark batter enriched with macerated dried fruits, nuts, spices, butter, eggs, sugar, and rum. It is baked until dense and fragrant, then rested so the flavors deepen, and it is served in slices during the holiday season.";
