"recipe.vn_banh_xeo.info" = "Banh xeo is a traditional Vietnamese crispy rice batter pancake, commonly associated with southern Vietnam, filled with pork, shrimp, bean sprouts, and scallions. It is cooked to order, cut into pieces, and eaten wrapped with lettuce, herbs, and rice paper, then dipped in nuoc cham at family meals and casual gatherings.";
