"recipe.vn_bun_cha.info" = "Bun cha is a traditional Hanoi dish of charcoal-grilled pork patties and sliced pork belly served in a warm sweet-sour fish sauce broth with rice vermicelli, fresh herbs, and pickled green papaya and carrot. It is eaten by dipping noodles and herbs into the bowl with the grilled pork, commonly as a midday meal.";
