"recipe.vn_pho_bo.info" = "Pho bo is a traditional Vietnamese beef noodle soup with a long-simmered clear broth scented with charred onion, ginger, and warm spices, served with rice noodles, sliced beef, and fresh herbs. It is a complete meal commonly eaten for breakfast or lunch and served piping hot with lime and chili at the table.";
