"recipe.za_bobotie.drink.body" = "A medium-bodied South African red such as Pinotage or a soft Shiraz complements the warm spices and sweet-savoury profile without overpowering the custard topping. If you prefer white, choose a lightly oaked Chenin Blanc. Non-alcoholic pairing: rooibos iced tea with a squeeze of lemon.";
