"recipe.za_cape_malay_curry.info" = "Cape Malay chicken curry is a Cape Town classic with warmly perfumed spices, tender chicken and potatoes, and a subtle sweet-sour edge typical of Cape Malay cooking. It is traditionally served with fluffy basmati rice, flaky roti for scooping, and a fresh tomato-onion-cucumber sambal with banana to cool the palate.";
