"recipe.za_malva_pudding.drink.body" = "A lightly chilled Muscat or late-harvest dessert wine matches the caramelised sweetness and buttery sauce. If you prefer something less sweet, try a softly oaked Chenin Blanc. Non-alcoholic pairing: rooibos tea, served hot or iced.";
